
Ranger Help for: fortify
========================

SYNTAX:      fortify <direction>
USAGE:       forest,plains,swamp,desert,jungle,hills,road,beach,
             underground,mountain,arctic,barren
SLOT COST:   5
BASE SP:     30 sp
SKILL TYPE:  defensive

SUMMARY:    
This skill allows a Ranger to gather materials from the surrounding
terrain and build a blockade or structure in one direction. The
blockade can be circumvented by 'trashing' it, allowing passage.
How strong or how much of a beating a blockade can take will depend
on how proficient a Ranger is at building them. Once a blockade is
built, other Rangers will be able to pass through it, since they
understand the nature of blockades.

